 "blurb": "Arms Warrior earns its raid spot with Blood Frenzy — a flat 4% physical damage buff for every melee in the group — while slam-weaving between swings for respectable personal numbers. The gear plan chases 2.2%+ weapon-speed two-handers and hit/expertise caps before raw strength. This Phase 2 snapshot aggregates 277 top DPS parses from Serpentshrine Cavern and Tempest Keep; the highest-consensus pick is Pendant of the Perilous at 75% usage.",
 "statPriorityRationale": "Arms in raids is a support DPS built around keeping Blood Frenzy's 4% physical damage buff active — you cap hit and expertise first because a dodged Mortal Strike is a rage crisis, then stack strength for slam-weave throughput.",
